msgctxt "124_Saejima"
msgid "Lotta homeless folks around."
msgstr "Muchos sin techo, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "136_Kido"
msgid "This is kind of their turf. We're the squatters down here."
msgstr "Sí, de hecho, este lugar les pertenece a ellos."

